orbitSensitivity.title: Orbit Sensitivity
orbitSensitivity.description: How fast the camera moves around the orbit. Higher is faster

camera.description: Optional, assign a camera entity, otherwise one is created

power.description: Adjusts the speed of player movement

pickAreaScale.title: Pick Area Scale
pickAreaScale.description: 1 is more accurate but worse performance. 0.01 is best performance but least accurate. 0.25 is the default.

layerNames.title: Layers Names
layerNames.description: Layer names from which objects will be picked from.
